{"tid":2145164,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"小妹想通了，想入OU","createTime":"2020-08-08T02:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T04:51:32.000Z","uid":312744,"like":58,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7cd1b8fffcd5143a898801ed41dd4af89fb857","tid":2145164,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:11:46.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。<br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"c35e4c98fbd0971fc48d177e81ca11b37fa340b4","tid":2145164,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:12:43.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"0782752d7830d20123aa6067b3a66b6c72f4e526","tid":2145164,"uid":200070,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"條友最後讀左psy nurse好似做埋護士<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />OU護理就係驗身唔驗腦 咩人都入得 公廁咁<br />\n楊生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441ec7fc7898f39c5b7537f031e90266a53b540e","tid":2145164,"uid":360830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"太勁了！！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7efb9838750777051712d902a8fbaa1ee0ddb6","tid":2145164,"uid":190789,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"入ou 個啲，除咗nursing 有邊啲搵到工"},{"pid":"6ccd40dedb73b54c6fed977a29db11c3e794d71e","tid":2145164,"uid":228143,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:14:31.000Z","msg":"條友好似做左護士啦<br />\n<br />\n月入都高過唔少當年笑佢既人<br />\n<br />\n真係睇科重要過睇咩學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown